title: Concept Learning and Action Recognition System
description: Developed a computer vision system using PyTorch to identify objects in images and generate human-readable text explanations detailing the reasoning behind the identification process. Analyzed video frames to recognize the subject and object of each action, predicting subsequent movements based on contextual understanding. Implemented and fine-tuned advanced machine learning models to improve action prediction accuracy and enhance the transparency of reasoning processes.

title: Random Forest Regressor
description: Perform Exploratory Data Analysis on the relation between sugar and protein and recipe.rating Predict Recipe rating used random forest regressor. Fin-tuning machine learning model using grid-search and cross-validation

title: Data Scientist Salary Prediction
description: Perform Exploratory Data Analysis on the relation between Data Scientist salary and remote working status and experience level. Implement multiple linear regression to make prediction of salary. Compare the salary growth rate between data scientist and other occupations. Address the Ethics and Privacy of the data collection process and project

title: Solar system model
description: Using C++ and OpenGL to create an animated solar system model. Implemented revolving and rotating of the earth and the moon

title: Huffman Tree Compression
description: Using C++ implement file compression using Huffman Tree. Created extremely efficient method to store the Huffman Tree, using at most 10 bits per distinct letter.
